Project Plan for Building an NFT Marketplace

Introduction: The goal of this project is to build a web3-based NFT marketplace. The marketplace should facilitate the buying and selling of unique digital assets such as art, music, and videos as NFTs (Non-Fungible Tokens). This project plan outlines the development process, milestones, and deadlines for each development phase.

Phase 1: Planning & Research (2 weeks)

